{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every 20 minutes you-- they turn around, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think-- I think about four or six.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, four or six.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Four.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after 20 minutes you turn them around, and 30 minutes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you put more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were just putting the corpse up to the elevator to the ovens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the-- the other people there-- two, three of them-- they take over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew their names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember them now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were pretty good, the relationships, you know, about with us, because I think they were the ones-- that there were a couple of them, they were Germans or something, and-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But most of the capos, they were with us in the number 2, crematorium 2, were pretty good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We already-- when I was there, there was already capos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CHUCKLING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, there were, you know, in each crematorium, there were-- there were about two or three.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were general capo was one by the name of Kaminsky that was a-- was very good one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at they end, they kill him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the SS kill him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he never-- whenever the Germans asked him, he never revealed names or anything else, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was a pretty good man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it didn't last at-- at the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the revolution, I think, they didn't-- he-- the Germans were talking to him, but he never revealed any names, whoever was-- who was in the revolution, who did that with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally they put him in the oven himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we had only two SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of them was from Holland, which is pretty-- was good enough.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other was a very bad man, you know, that I know [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
